					<div class="col-md-12">
						<p>Welcome to <b>pls enjoy tournament</b>! This is the official site for the tournament. Please check this site regularly during the competition, as updates, mappool, and rankings will all be posted here. You may also reference <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UkOqUm2Q1tkKV3v9cCRE-GludaWwf9_GuegeZw4FZF8/edit" target="_blank">this Google doc</a> for information.</p>
						<p>Registration for this tournament will take place on this site, rather than through the forum. The registration form will open on <b>December 13</b>.</p>
						<div class="page-header">
							<h4>Updates</h4>
						</div>
