							<li>Group Stage: weekends of <b>January 2</b> and <b>January 9</b></li>
							<li>Round of 8 (Quarterfinals): weekend of <b>January 16</b></li>
							<li>Round of 4 (Semifinals): weekend of <b>January 23</b></li>
							<li>Round of 2 (Finals): weekend of <b>January 30</b></li>
